      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber">1823.570-2</ph> Contract clause.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p xtrc="P">The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="Section_1852_223_74_T48_60423441158"
                  href="Section_1852_223_74_T48_60423441158.dita#Section_1852_223_74_T48_60423441158">1852.223-74</xref>, Drug- and Alcohol-Free Workforce, in all solicitations and contracts exceeding $5 million in which work is performed by an employee in a sensitive position. However, the contracting officer shall not insert the clause at <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="Section_1852_223_74_T48_60423441158"
                  href="Section_1852_223_74_T48_60423441158.dita#Section_1852_223_74_T48_60423441158">1852.223-74</xref> in solicitations and contracts for commercial items.
</p>
